  "texts": [
    "As ML applications become increasingly ubiquitous, concerns about data privacy and security have also grown.",
    "PPML safeguards data confidentiality in compliance with data protection regulations.",
    "The aim is to develop models that can operate on encrypted or anonymized data, preventing unauthorized access to sensitive information.",
    "By combining decentralized data access for ML training and PETs, PPML enables organizations to build, deploy, and manage ML models reliably and securely (Mothukuri et al. 2021).",
